          "type": "explanation",
          "name": "Motion blur parameters:",
          "definition": "num taps:............. # of taps to take; should be around 5, max is 20. impacts performance greatly!!\nmax {x,y}:............ max amount to blur [good values are 0 - 0.2]\nscale {x,y}:.......... scale amount to blur based on motion [good values are 0 - 0.2]\nscale {x,y}:.......... scale amount to blur based on motion [good values are 0 - 0.2]\ncenter falloff:....... rate at which motion blur falls off towards the center of the screen [good values are 0.1 - 5.0]\nexpected dt:.......... expected time per tick, in seconds (used to correct motion blur in fast/slow frames)\n"
